fn.p: Ddf: denominator degrees of freedom; Ndf: numerator degrees of freedom. Values in bold indicate effects were significant ( p < 0.05). Posthoc tests (Tukey's HSD) performed where effects were significant at p < 0.05. NS is nonsignificant ( p > 0.1).
Data were square root transformed to achieve homogeneity of variance.
Outliers were removed to achieve homogeneity of variance.
